<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Вход - CitiVoice</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/spatial.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #030303;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .auth-bg {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 20% 25%, rgba(224, 255, 79, 0.08), transparent 45%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(40, 120, 255, 0.08), transparent 45%);
        }

        .auth-shell {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: grid;
            place-items: center;
            padding: 130px 20px 40px;
        }

        .auth-card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 460px;
            background: rgba(12, 14, 24, 0.82);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border-radius: 30px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(26px);
            box-shadow: 0 26px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
            padding: 34px;
        }

        .auth-top {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .auth-title {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 34px;
            line-height: 1.05;
            letter-spacing: -0.8px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .auth-subtitle {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .auth-switch {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 18px;
        }

        .switch-pill {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        }

        .switch-pill.active {
            color: #0a0b10;
            background: #E0FF4F;
            border-color: rgba(224, 255, 79, 0.75);
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .form-label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 7px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.35px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-size: 15px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            outline: none;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .form-control::placeholder {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: #E0FF4F;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(224, 255, 79, 0.14);
        }

        .btn-action {
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 8px;
            background: #E0FF4F;
            color: #0b0d12;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.2s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(224, 255, 79, 0.25);
        }

        .btn-action:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 26px rgba(224, 255, 79, 0.35);
        }

        .error-message {
            color: #ff7676;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            background: rgba(255, 79, 79, 0.12);
            padding: 11px 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 79, 79, 0.24);
        }

        .helper-text {
            margin-top: 12px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52);
            text-align: center;
        }

        @media (max-width: 520px) {
            .auth-card {
                padding: 26px 20px;
                border-radius: 22px;
            }

            .auth-title {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="auth-bg"></div>

    <nav class="spatial-nav glass-panel">
        <div class="nav-brand">
            <a href="/" style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; text-decoration:none; color:inherit;">
                <img src="/images/logo-icon.png" alt="Logo" style="height:24px;">CitiVoice
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/places">Места</a>
            <a href="/routes">Маршруты</a>
            <a href="/game">Игра</a>
            <a href="/map">Карта</a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-user">
            <a href="<%= locals.user ? '/profile' : '/login' %>" style="color: inherit;">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                    <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="auth-shell">
        <div class="auth-card">
            <div class="auth-top">
                <h1 class="auth-title">Вход</h1>
                <p class="auth-subtitle">Войдите в аккаунт, чтобы продолжить исследование маршрутов и мест.</p>
                <div class="auth-switch">
                    <a href="/login" class="switch-pill active">Вход</a>
                    <a href="/register" class="switch-pill">Регистрация</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <% if (locals.error) { %>
                <div class="error-message">
                    <%= error %>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                    <form action="/login" method="POST">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Email или логин</label>
                            <input type="text" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="name@example.com"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Пароль</label>
                            <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Введите пароль"
                                required>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-action">Войти</button>
                    </form>

                    <div class="helper-text">Если аккаунта нет, создайте его во вкладке «Регистрация».</div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>